      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "韩擒虎",
        "杨戈",
        "杨素"
      ],
      "text": "一同前往。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016001_e00011",
      "play_id": "01016001",
      "scene_id": "01016001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "宇文化及"
      ],
      "text": "香烟缭绕，圣驾临朝。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016001_e00012",
      "play_id": "01016001",
      "scene_id": "01016001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "〖牌子〗。〖小开门〗。四太监同上，杨广上。",
      "text_length": 21
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016001_e00013",
      "play_id": "01016001",
      "scene_id": "01016001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "引子",
      "speakers": [
        "杨广"
      ],
      "text": "凤阁龙楼，万古千秋。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016001_e00014",
      "play_id": "01016001",
      "scene_id": "01016001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "杨广"
      ],
      "text": "玉漏催残报晓筹，佩声归到凤池头。九天闾阖开宫殿，万国衣冠拜冕旒。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016001_e00015",
      "play_id": "01016001",
      "scene_id": "01016001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨广"
      ],
      "text": "孤王杨广。先皇宴驾，孤王登基，倒也风调雨顺，国泰民安。今当早朝。众卿，",
      "text_length": 35
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016001_e00016",
      "play_id": "01016001",
      "scene_id": "01016001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "宇文化及",
        "韩擒虎",
        "杨戈",
        "杨素"
      ],
      "text": "万岁。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016001_e00017",
      "play_id": "01016001",
      "scene_id": "01016001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨广"
      ],
      "text": "有本早奏，无本退班。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016001_e00018",
      "play_id": "01016001",
      "scene_id": "01016001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "宇文化及"
      ],
      "text": "臣启万岁：今当先帝宴驾，新君登基，满朝文武，俱来朝贺，惟有伍建章，不见来朝，望万岁降旨治罪。",
      "text_length": 46
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016001_e00019",
      "play_id": "01016001",
      "scene_id": "01016001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨广"
      ],
      "text": "想那伍建章，乃是三朝元老，孤王也不降罪于他，由他去罢。",
      "text_length": 27
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016001_e00020",
      "play_id": "01016001",
      "scene_id": "01016001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "宇文化及"
      ],
      "text": "万岁若不降旨治罪，臣恐满朝文武不服。",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016001_e00021",
      "play_id": "01016001",
      "scene_id": "01016001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨广"
      ],
      "text": "内侍，宣伍建章上殿。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016001_e00022",
      "play_id": "01016001",
      "scene_id": "01016001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "内侍"
      ],
      "text": "万岁有旨：伍建章上殿。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016001_e00023",
      "play_id": "01016001",
      "scene_id": "01016001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "内白",
      "speakers": [
        "伍建章"
      ],
      "text": "来也。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016001_e00024",
      "play_id": "01016001",
      "scene_id": "01016001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "伍建章上。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016001_e00025",
      "play_id": "01016001",
      "scene_id": "01016001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "伍建章"
      ],
      "text": "忽听金殿一声吵，倒叫老夫怒眉梢。将身一来在金殿道，只见昏王在当朝。",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016001_e00026",
      "play_id": "01016001",
      "scene_id": "01016001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "伍建章"
      ],
      "text": "老夫，伍建章。正在朝房，挂孝成服，祭奠先帝，闻听金殿宣召，不免上得金殿，将昏王十大罪恶，一一宣扬。纵然将我千刀万剐，也落个青史名标，万代流芳也！",
      "text_length": 72
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016001_e00027",
      "play_id": "01016001",
      "scene_id": "01016001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "伍建章"
      ],
      "text": "昏王无道乱朝纲，赛过夏桀、商纣王。欺母奸妹天良丧，诛兄盗嫂败伦常。迈步且把金殿上，且听昏王说端详。",
      "text_length": 49
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016001_e00028",
      "play_id": "01016001",
      "scene_id": "01016001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨广"
      ],
      "text": "伍建章，今当先帝宴驾，孤王登基，满朝文武，均来朝贺。惟有你这老儿，不来朝贺，你就有欺君之罪。本当加罪于你，念在你是三朝元老，姑且饶恕。命你在金殿之上，替孤写下草诏，颁行天下。待等颁诏回来，将功折罪。",
      "text_length": 99
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016001_e00029",
      "play_id": "01016001",
      "scene_id": "01016001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "伍建章"
      ],
      "text": "先帝呀，先帝！你龙归沧海，昏王登基，混乱朝纲，败坏伦常，与夏桀、商纣、楚平王一样。我不免就将他十大罪恶，写在诏上，拚着我老命不要，辱骂他一番，便了。",
      "text_length": 74
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016001_e00030",
      "play_id": "01016001",
      "scene_id": "01016001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮原板",
      "speakers": [
        "伍建章"
      ],
      "text": "都只为老王爷龙归天上，不料这小昏王他坐了朝堂。恨只恨韩擒虎做事卤莽，最可恨宇文化及霸占朝纲。还有那贼杨素狗奸党，助纣为虐败坏伦常。此时间不由我怒冲心上，拚着我老性命付与汪洋。我怒气不息把公案上，",
      "text_length": 97
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016001_e00031",
      "play_id": "01016001",
      "scene_id": "01016001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "伍建章"
      ],
      "text": "我这里提羊毫细写一桩。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016001_e00032",
      "play_id": "01016001",
      "scene_id": "01016001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "伍建章"
      ],
      "text": "诏曰：老王宴驾，新君嗣位；昏慵无道，搅乱朝纲。欺母奸妹，杀兄盗嫂；子纳父妃，败坏伦常。天良何在？人神之所共嫉，天地之所不容！天下之人，恨不得食尔之肉。为此草诏天下。",
      "text_length": 82
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016001_e00033",
      "play_id": "01016001",
      "scene_id": "01016001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "内侍呈诏与杨广。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016001_e00034",
      "play_id": "01016001",
      "scene_id": "01016001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "曰",
      "speakers": [
        "杨广"
      ],
      "text": "“诏曰，老王宴驾，新君嗣位；昏慵无道，搅乱朝纲。欺母奸妹，杀兄盗嫂；子纳父妃，败坏伦常。天良何在？人神之所共嫉，天地之所不容！天下之人，恨不得食尔之肉。为此草诏天下。”呀呀呸！胆大伍建章，擅敢辱骂孤家，恨不得将尔碎尸万段！",
      "text_length": 111
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016001_e00035",
      "play_id": "01016001",
      "scene_id": "01016001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "宇文化及"
      ],
      "text": "启万岁：念伍建章，乃是三朝元老，将他敲牙割舌，也就够了。",
      "text_length": 28
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016001_e00036",
      "play_id": "01016001",
      "scene_id": "01016001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 36,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨广"
      ],
      "text": "但凭卿家。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016001_e00037",
      "play_id": "01016001",
      "scene_id": "01016001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 37,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "宇文化及"
      ],
      "text": "万岁有旨：将伍建章敲牙割舌。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016001_e00038",
      "play_id": "01016001",
      "scene_id": "01016001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 38,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "伍建章"
      ],
      "text": "哦。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016001_e00039",
      "play_id": "01016001",
      "scene_id": "01016001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 39,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "伍建章"
      ],
      "text": "听说是割舌要敲牙，三朝元老染黄沙。眼望九泉哭殿下，先王爷吓！我要到阴曹府把他抓。",
      "text_length": 40
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016001_e00040",
      "play_id": "01016001",
      "scene_id": "01016001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 40,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "伍建章下。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016001_e00041",
      "play_id": "01016001",
      "scene_id": "01016001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 41,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "宇文化及"
      ],
      "text": "臣启万岁：伍建章，他有一子，名唤伍云昭，现在领兵，镇守南阳。此人武艺高强，倘若他带兵前来，反上金殿，只怕万岁性命难保。",
      "text_length": 59
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016001_e00042",
      "play_id": "01016001",
      "scene_id": "01016001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 42,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨广"
      ],
      "text": "韩擒虎听令：命你带领三千人马，去至南阳，捉拿伍云召，进京问罪。",
      "text_length": 31
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016001_e00043",
      "play_id": "01016001",
      "scene_id": "01016001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 43,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "韩擒虎"
      ],
      "text": "领旨。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016001_e00044",
      "play_id": "01016001",
      "scene_id": "01016001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 44,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨广"
      ],
      "text": "宇文化及听令：命宇文成都，带领三千人马，解押粮草，军前听用，帮同韩擒虎，捉拿伍云昭进京。领旨下殿。",
      "text_length": 49
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016001_e00045",
      "play_id": "01016001",
      "scene_id": "01016001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 45,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "宇文化及"
      ],
      "text": "领旨。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016001_e00046",
      "play_id": "01016001",
      "scene_id": "01016001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 46,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "众人同下。",
      "text_length": 5
    }
  ],
  "roles_inferred": true
}